N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4403.3 - Organizational plan of the corporation

State Regulations

Each corporation shall submit detailed information
concerning the structure, administration and staff arrangements of the
corporation, including proposed rates of compensation for its personnel and
position descriptions therefor. Notes
